# GitHub Linguist — DirCompareAndSync-Releases
# O repo publico distribui binarios; estas regras fazem a barra "Languages"
# reflectir as tecnologias reais da aplicacao (ver pasta stack/).

# Pagina GitHub Pages e documentacao do site
docs/** linguist-documentation
*.html linguist-documentation
README.md linguist-documentation
google*.html linguist-documentation

# Capturas de ecrã
docs/screenshots/** linguist-generated

# Notas de versao em JSON (nao e codigo)
release-notes.json linguist-detectable=false

# Interface Avalonia (.axaml)
stack/**/*.axaml linguist-language=Avalonia
stack/README.md linguist-documentation
